text: Juliet Thompson (born December 20, 1967) is an American rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. She graduated from Harvard University and Stanford University. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Louisville, Kentucky Category:Harvard Crimson rowers Category:Stanford University alumni
